<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>扫码登录 - 心语视界</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f7; }
</style>
<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="30">
</head>
<body class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
<div class="text-center">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">心语视界</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">首次使用需要扫码登录小红书</p>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg max-w-sm mx-auto">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">请使用小红书 App 扫描二维码</p>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl w-64 h-64 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">请查看</p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-4">
      浏览器正在尝试登录中...<br>
      请打开 <code class="text-blue-500">output/screenshots/</code> 查看登录页面截图<br>
      扫码后页面将自动跳转
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-6">登录态会保存在 Cookie 中, 重启后无需重新登录</p>
</div>
<script>
setInterval(async () => {
  try {
    const r = await fetch('/api/stats');
    if (r.ok) { location.href = '/'; }
  } catch(e) {}
}, 5000);
</script>
</body>
</html>
